General.Name: Cardno Limited
General.Description: Cardno Limited, a professional environmental services company, engages in the development and improvement of physical and social infrastructure for communities in Ecuador and Peru. It operates through Latin America and Other Segments. The company provides engineering and consulting services in Latin America. Cardno Limited was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Sydney, Australia.
